<P>THE Antient Te&s;timony OF THE PEOPLE CALLED QUAKERS, REVIV'D: By the Order and Approbation of the YEARLY MEETING held for the Province of <HI>Penn&s;ylvania</HI> and <HI>Jer&s;eys.</HI> 1722.</P>
<P><HI>PHILADELPHIA:</HI> Printed by <HI>Andrew Bradford</HI> at the Sign of the Bible in <HI>Second-&s;treet.</HI> 1723.</P>
</DIV1>
